WEBVTT

00:00:00.006 --> 00:01:00.006

00:01:30.220 --> 00:01:32.980
[Episode 09]

00:01:35.150 --> 00:01:36.870
I don't really have any demands.

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.200
I just hope

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:41.480
you convince my mother-in-law

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:43.870
to stay in Shenzhen with me.

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:45.400
We've already

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:47.120
asked her.

00:01:47.560 --> 00:01:49.480
She said she can't trouble you

00:01:49.760 --> 00:01:51.070
and drag you down.

00:01:52.280 --> 00:01:53.560
But she's blind.

00:01:54.480 --> 00:01:56.070
She needs someone to take care of her.

00:01:56.400 --> 00:01:57.950
She's the mother of a martyr.

00:01:58.680 --> 00:02:01.230
The government will
take full responsibility.

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:03.640
Our town's nursing home

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:04.950
has prepared

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:06.000
a private room for her.

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:08.680
Yet she insists on
staying in a triple room.

00:02:09.150 --> 00:02:09.960
Even though

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:11.800
she's blind,

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:13.710
she can still work

00:02:14.240 --> 00:02:14.910
and cook.

00:02:15.310 --> 00:02:17.750
Everyone around here

00:02:18.190 --> 00:02:19.750
knows her as a tough woman.

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.470
We should respect her wishes.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:38.240
Alright.

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:41.030
Then I have a request.

00:02:41.960 --> 00:02:42.560
Go ahead.

00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:52.190
My mother-in-law gave me this.

00:02:52.870 --> 00:02:53.840
It's the allowance

00:02:55.240 --> 00:02:56.960
Shuchun sent over the years.

00:03:00.750 --> 00:03:02.430
Please donate it to the nursing home.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:30.120
Liu,

00:03:31.870 --> 00:03:32.590
pay more attention

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.400
to Li Juan these days.

00:03:36.470 --> 00:03:37.470
Mr. Zhou

00:03:38.310 --> 00:03:39.960
was our best friend.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:43.680
Rest... rest assured, Mr. Hu.

00:04:00.960 --> 00:04:01.870
Take it.

00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:04.240
What medicine?

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:05.430
I'm not sick.

00:04:05.750 --> 00:04:06.840
I got it from the clinic.

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.240
Specially for a broken heart.

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:12.960
Well, take two.

00:04:13.190 --> 00:04:14.280
No need.

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:16.720
If you consider us friends,

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:17.560
take it.

00:04:19.190 --> 00:04:20.040
Right.

00:04:20.190 --> 00:04:21.120
Just listen to her.

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:22.800
Okay?

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:01.310
Why is Juan's fate so cruel?

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:06.630
I'm really heartbroken.

00:05:11.310 --> 00:05:13.920
I wish I could bear it for her.

00:06:11.310 --> 00:06:12.390
What do we do?

00:06:24.070 --> 00:06:24.680
Juan.

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:26.800
You're back.

00:06:30.950 --> 00:06:32.160
Those were sleeping pills, huh?

00:06:32.870 --> 00:06:33.870
I slept for so long.

00:06:35.870 --> 00:06:36.950
Didn't Wanzhi leave you

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.070
a note?

00:06:38.270 --> 00:06:39.310
You need some good rest.

00:06:39.630 --> 00:06:40.480
How come you washed

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:42.160
our sheets?

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:43.120
Wanzhi,

00:06:43.430 --> 00:06:45.120
give her two more pills.

00:06:45.680 --> 00:06:46.310
No worries.

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:48.160
I'll sleep like a baby tonight

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.390
and won't bother you again.

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:52.480
Mr. Zhou said

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:54.190
if you have the will,

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:56.510
you can get through anything.

00:06:57.870 --> 00:06:58.950
Let alone sleep.

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:03.160
Don't scare me.

00:07:04.630 --> 00:07:05.870
What's wrong with you?

00:07:07.190 --> 00:07:07.600
Wait,

00:07:08.430 --> 00:07:09.800
is it really hitting you hard?

00:07:10.950 --> 00:07:12.000
Oh, shut up.

00:07:17.720 --> 00:07:18.360
Li Juan,

00:07:20.190 --> 00:07:21.360
Mr. Zhou was right.

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.070
All hardships

00:07:25.390 --> 00:07:26.360
will pass.

00:07:28.070 --> 00:07:28.600
I know.

00:07:31.430 --> 00:07:32.310
I have to stay strong.

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:34.160
My mother-in-law,

00:07:34.630 --> 00:07:35.160
my mom,

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:37.360
and my siblings all depend on me.

00:07:37.680 --> 00:07:38.560
And us!

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:40.830
To me, you're the strongest person.

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:49.870
You bought a pager?

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:51.720
No.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.120
A friend gave it.

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:55.240
I'm gonna return this call.

00:08:27.680 --> 00:08:28.190
Qian,

00:08:28.510 --> 00:08:29.430
I missed you so much!

00:08:34.550 --> 00:08:35.360
You're bad.

00:08:35.630 --> 00:08:36.630
It's broad daylight!

00:08:37.150 --> 00:08:38.440
No one else is here now.

00:08:38.630 --> 00:08:39.390
It's safe.

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:42.630
They're back.

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.150
We need to be careful.

00:08:44.600 --> 00:08:45.750
I am being careful!

00:08:46.320 --> 00:08:47.600
I even paged you for this date.

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:48.390
Besides,

00:08:48.750 --> 00:08:49.510
we're official.

00:08:49.910 --> 00:08:50.870
Why be afraid?

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:52.550
You might not be, but I am.

00:08:55.870 --> 00:08:57.960
You know how picky I am.

00:08:58.600 --> 00:08:59.510
But now,

00:08:59.870 --> 00:09:01.840
I've fallen for you.

00:09:03.030 --> 00:09:04.150
I'm a total goner!

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:05.270
I hate that you didn't

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:06.910
fall for me sooner.

00:10:08.270 --> 00:10:10.750
♪Rose, rose♪

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:17.750
♪I love you with an aching heart♪

00:10:23.630 --> 00:10:24.670
Why look at me

00:10:24.670 --> 00:10:25.550
like this?

00:10:26.030 --> 00:10:26.870
Tell us honestly.

00:10:27.390 --> 00:10:28.630
When did you two get together?

00:10:29.720 --> 00:10:31.480
What...

00:10:31.550 --> 00:10:33.480
Get... get together?

00:10:33.750 --> 00:10:34.670
Who?

00:10:34.670 --> 00:10:35.510
You and Liu Zhu!

00:10:35.870 --> 00:10:36.480
Keep hiding it,

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.390
and we're not friends.

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:38.510
No!

00:10:38.630 --> 00:10:40.150
We promised to be friends forever.

00:10:40.200 --> 00:10:41.320
I treasure it.

00:10:41.720 --> 00:10:43.030
Then out with it.

00:10:48.670 --> 00:10:49.440
Well,

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:52.630
you accompanied her back.

00:10:53.480 --> 00:10:55.550
I was lonely.

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:57.720
It's his fault. He insisted on drinking.

00:10:58.270 --> 00:10:59.840
As we drank,

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:02.150
we just started talking.

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:03.960
And then,

00:11:04.870 --> 00:11:06.870
he didn't seem so bad.

00:11:09.270 --> 00:11:11.360
Loneliness is to blame.

00:11:12.910 --> 00:11:13.550
I...

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:17.320
Qian, honestly,

00:11:18.440 --> 00:11:18.960
I think

00:11:19.030 --> 00:11:20.320
you and Zhu are a good match.

00:11:20.750 --> 00:11:22.200
We're not a match!

00:11:23.120 --> 00:11:23.670
Anyway,

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:25.000
I gotta say this though.

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:27.270
I didn't think much

00:11:27.390 --> 00:11:28.270
of him before.

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:30.870
But after we started dating,

00:11:31.750 --> 00:11:33.630
I saw he's pretty caring.

00:11:34.510 --> 00:11:35.080
By the way,

00:11:35.390 --> 00:11:36.910
his family has some savings.

00:11:39.360 --> 00:11:39.840
Qian,

00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:41.080
I have to warn you.

00:11:41.360 --> 00:11:42.550
Zhu and Liu

00:11:42.600 --> 00:11:43.480
are honest.

00:11:43.910 --> 00:11:45.320
Don't go changing your mind.

00:11:45.600 --> 00:11:47.000
What do you mean?

00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:47.630
They're honest,

00:11:47.630 --> 00:11:48.910
and I'm not?

00:11:57.720 --> 00:11:58.630
What's wrong?

00:11:59.790 --> 00:12:00.390
Gosh.

00:12:02.790 --> 00:12:03.790
What's wrong with you?

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:06.670
Don't even ask.

00:12:08.030 --> 00:12:09.840
Can't fake it this time.

00:12:13.080 --> 00:12:13.630
Qian,

00:12:15.320 --> 00:12:16.440
are you pregnant?

00:12:18.790 --> 00:12:19.840
Maybe.

00:12:20.390 --> 00:12:21.270
Didn't think

00:12:21.550 --> 00:12:22.840
Zhu had it in him.

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:24.960
Hao Qianqian,

00:12:25.840 --> 00:12:26.550
you're lying.

00:12:27.150 --> 00:12:28.440
I'm not.

00:12:28.440 --> 00:12:29.320
Zhu is

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:30.550
my only boyfriend.

00:12:31.510 --> 00:12:32.510
You just said

00:12:32.510 --> 00:12:33.720
loneliness was to blame.

00:12:33.910 --> 00:12:35.670
But we were only gone a few days!

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.390
Morning sickness

00:12:37.390 --> 00:12:39.000
starts at six weeks.

00:12:39.240 --> 00:12:39.750
When did you

00:12:39.750 --> 00:12:40.630
get together with Zhu?

00:12:40.960 --> 00:12:41.600
Confess again.

00:12:41.750 --> 00:12:42.200
I...

00:12:42.670 --> 00:12:43.910
Are you a cop?

00:12:44.080 --> 00:12:45.550
Treating me like a criminal.

00:12:46.080 --> 00:12:47.510
You've never been pregnant.

00:12:47.550 --> 00:12:49.080
What do you know?

00:12:49.270 --> 00:12:50.000
My mom

00:12:50.030 --> 00:12:51.720
was the best gynecologist in Yu County.

00:12:51.910 --> 00:12:53.150
So I picked it up.

00:12:53.200 --> 00:12:53.910
You can't fool me.

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:56.720
Well, fine.

00:12:58.550 --> 00:12:59.790
It was

00:13:00.030 --> 00:13:00.960
when Liu

00:13:01.270 --> 00:13:02.440
sent us

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:03.240
to buy groceries.

00:13:03.240 --> 00:13:03.910
It was him.

00:13:04.150 --> 00:13:05.510
Kept buying me things

00:13:05.630 --> 00:13:06.600
to tempt me.

00:13:08.030 --> 00:13:08.720
Qian,

00:13:09.200 --> 00:13:10.080
then you...

00:13:10.840 --> 00:13:12.270
Now that this has happened,

00:13:12.840 --> 00:13:14.120
what are you gonna do?

00:13:14.840 --> 00:13:17.200
Going to his hometown to get married.

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:19.150
We just decided today.

00:13:20.360 --> 00:13:21.480
I didn't even figure out

00:13:21.870 --> 00:13:23.910
how to tell you two.

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:28.080
Congratulations,

00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:29.440
Zhu's wife.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:30.840
What?

00:13:30.960 --> 00:13:31.870
That sounds awful!

00:13:33.080 --> 00:13:33.600
Hey!

00:13:33.720 --> 00:13:35.120
Well, I'll stop, Zhu's wife.

00:13:36.150 --> 00:13:36.720
Qian!

00:13:36.750 --> 00:13:37.270
Fang Wanzhi!

00:13:37.270 --> 00:13:38.510
You'll hurt the baby.

00:13:38.510 --> 00:13:39.600
Come on. Don't tease her.

00:13:39.600 --> 00:13:40.670
That's a good one.

00:13:40.870 --> 00:13:42.320
It isn't!

00:13:42.550 --> 00:13:43.360
Qian!

00:13:58.270 --> 00:13:59.480
Wanzhi.

00:14:00.390 --> 00:14:01.200
Wanzhi.

00:14:01.240 --> 00:14:02.120
Don't run.

00:14:02.510 --> 00:14:03.480
It's okay.

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:04.390
Your letter.

00:14:05.390 --> 00:14:06.080
Thanks.

00:14:17.910 --> 00:14:18.550
Let me see.

00:14:20.550 --> 00:14:21.600
Juan!

00:14:22.030 --> 00:14:22.720
Come here!

00:14:25.150 --> 00:14:25.720
Look.

00:14:26.510 --> 00:14:27.360
Gosh!

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:32.790
What's wrong?

00:14:35.080 --> 00:14:36.320
Whenever I see uniform,

00:14:37.320 --> 00:14:38.670
I think of Mr. Zhou.

00:14:40.790 --> 00:14:41.600
Well, fine.

00:14:42.120 --> 00:14:44.150
He's really handsome.

00:14:46.550 --> 00:14:47.720
Don't even think about it.

00:14:48.510 --> 00:14:49.790
What's wrong with thinking?

00:14:50.270 --> 00:14:52.240
I know it's too late now.

00:14:52.510 --> 00:14:53.240
What a pity.

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:55.000
Who's he?

00:14:55.670 --> 00:14:56.840
My nephew, Yang Hui.

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:00.440
The one you send money to?

00:15:00.960 --> 00:15:01.630
Not bad.

00:15:01.670 --> 00:15:03.030
He's got some decency.

00:15:03.150 --> 00:15:04.120
At least he sent you

00:15:04.150 --> 00:15:05.870
a photo after becoming a soldier.

00:15:07.120 --> 00:15:08.240
He looks young.

00:15:08.630 --> 00:15:09.270
Maybe we could

00:15:09.440 --> 00:15:10.750
set him up with Juan.

00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:11.960
Hao Qianqian!

00:15:12.600 --> 00:15:13.750
Don't bullshit!

00:15:14.080 --> 00:15:15.030
Mr. Zhou is gone.

00:15:15.030 --> 00:15:15.840
You don't have to

00:15:15.840 --> 00:15:16.440
be alone.

00:15:16.440 --> 00:15:17.150
Shut up!

00:15:23.270 --> 00:15:23.870
Qian,

00:15:24.510 --> 00:15:25.390
you're going too far.

00:15:26.390 --> 00:15:27.600
Come on.

00:15:27.750 --> 00:15:29.510
Juan can't stay like this forever.

00:15:32.630 --> 00:15:33.150
(Auntie,)

00:15:33.910 --> 00:15:35.150
(I have)

00:15:35.150 --> 00:15:36.360
(officially joined)

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:37.200
(the PLA Air Force.)

00:15:37.480 --> 00:15:39.480
(Sending a photo as a souvenir.)

00:15:40.600 --> 00:15:41.550
(I will)

00:15:42.150 --> 00:15:43.080
(never forget)

00:15:43.910 --> 00:15:44.870
(your kindness.)

00:15:47.670 --> 00:15:49.030
Oh, Wanzhi,

00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:51.510
you've been reading it all afternoon.

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:54.000
I bet

00:15:55.080 --> 00:15:55.910
my nephew

00:15:55.910 --> 00:15:56.910
will be somebody.

00:15:58.360 --> 00:15:59.440
I was right to help him.

00:16:00.270 --> 00:16:01.480
Yeah.

00:16:58.390 --> 00:16:59.240
What are you doing?

00:16:59.360 --> 00:17:00.790
Swapping cards?

00:17:01.440 --> 00:17:02.360
We're family.

00:17:02.440 --> 00:17:03.600
Same difference.

00:17:03.600 --> 00:17:04.240
Exactly.

00:17:04.720 --> 00:17:05.240
Pay tribute.

00:17:05.790 --> 00:17:07.240
Give you a King, okay?

00:17:07.400 --> 00:17:07.880
No.

00:17:07.880 --> 00:17:09.160
You have a two, right?

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:10.960
I finally get a two.

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:12.400
Give it to you, and I'll lose.

00:17:12.750 --> 00:17:13.440
Hold on.

00:17:13.720 --> 00:17:14.680
Let me think.

00:17:17.200 --> 00:17:18.270
Did you two get tickets?

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:19.310
I got mine.

00:17:19.510 --> 00:17:20.440
Logistics helped.

00:17:21.030 --> 00:17:22.070
Early booking is a must.

00:17:22.400 --> 00:17:23.510
The Spring Festival travel rush.

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:25.310
What's that saying?

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:27.240
It's all about the railways.

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:28.510
And Shenzhen

00:17:28.750 --> 00:17:29.510
is at the heart

00:17:29.750 --> 00:17:30.830
of it all.

00:17:31.830 --> 00:17:32.350
Guess what?

00:17:32.350 --> 00:17:33.830
The station was completely packed.

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:36.640
Logistics helped with tickets.

00:17:36.790 --> 00:17:37.920
Why'd you go to the station?

00:17:38.510 --> 00:17:40.070
Just to get me a sleeper,

00:17:40.070 --> 00:17:41.590
he got squeezed so tight.

00:17:42.680 --> 00:17:44.510
Because I worry about you.

00:17:44.680 --> 00:17:46.310
You just worry about your kid.

00:17:46.960 --> 00:17:47.480
Here.

00:17:48.750 --> 00:17:50.110
Give me a three?

00:17:50.160 --> 00:17:51.750
I don't even have a four.

00:17:52.030 --> 00:17:52.960
Fang, did you get yours?

00:17:53.480 --> 00:17:54.030
No.

00:17:54.400 --> 00:17:55.550
I'll stay in Shenzhen.

00:17:55.590 --> 00:17:56.440
Not going anywhere.

00:17:56.920 --> 00:17:58.030
You're not going home?

00:17:58.510 --> 00:17:59.920
You have family, don't you?

00:18:00.680 --> 00:18:01.920
Is nobody calling you home?

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:03.110
Watch your mouth.

00:18:04.640 --> 00:18:05.110
They do.

00:18:05.790 --> 00:18:07.160
But I wanna use the break

00:18:07.160 --> 00:18:08.030
to look for a job.

00:18:08.310 --> 00:18:09.510
Shenzhen needs workers now.

00:18:09.590 --> 00:18:10.830
Might I could find a good one.

00:18:11.720 --> 00:18:13.160
Spending the holiday by yourself?

00:18:13.920 --> 00:18:14.640
Too bad.

00:18:15.070 --> 00:18:15.550
My dad and I

00:18:15.550 --> 00:18:17.030
aren't running the canteen.

00:18:17.240 --> 00:18:18.270
Or we'd keep you on.

00:18:18.880 --> 00:18:19.960
Don't be so full

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:20.830
of yourself.

00:18:20.830 --> 00:18:22.440
Wanzhi is capable.

00:18:22.680 --> 00:18:23.240
She won't

00:18:23.270 --> 00:18:24.590
work for you forever.

00:18:25.590 --> 00:18:26.790
Not like me.

00:18:26.920 --> 00:18:28.110
Wanzhi taught me a saying.

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:29.480
A single slip...

00:18:29.480 --> 00:18:30.240
Come on.

00:18:30.510 --> 00:18:32.200
You don't know how good you have it.

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:33.440
One more word, and I'll kick you.

00:18:33.750 --> 00:18:35.110
No kicking.

00:18:35.880 --> 00:18:36.590
I'm on your side.

00:18:36.590 --> 00:18:38.000
Can't you tell?

00:18:39.720 --> 00:18:40.240
Wanzhi,

00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.510
I'll go to my mother-in-law's,

00:18:41.880 --> 00:18:43.110
then head home.

00:18:43.550 --> 00:18:44.440
After Lantern Festival,

00:18:44.550 --> 00:18:45.550
I'll come back.

00:18:45.790 --> 00:18:47.480
Just over 20 days. Don't miss me.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:49.310
If you miss Qian,

00:18:49.480 --> 00:18:50.160
call her.

00:18:50.590 --> 00:18:51.960
We got a phone put in at home.

00:18:52.400 --> 00:18:53.550
So she wouldn't

00:18:53.790 --> 00:18:54.720
feel lonely.

00:18:56.110 --> 00:18:57.720
Five, six, seven, eight, nine.

00:18:58.440 --> 00:18:59.240
Can't beat that.

00:18:59.400 --> 00:19:00.640
God, who could?

00:19:01.510 --> 00:19:02.510
Not me.

00:19:18.030 --> 00:19:18.440
Dad,

00:19:19.270 --> 00:19:19.880
what's wrong?

00:19:22.240 --> 00:19:23.590
Finance has

00:19:24.440 --> 00:19:25.720
a new director.

00:19:26.720 --> 00:19:27.550
Won't acknowledge it.

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:28.960
He says

00:19:29.640 --> 00:19:32.590
he's never heard of a year-end bonus.

00:19:33.240 --> 00:19:34.270
What does it mean?

00:19:34.680 --> 00:19:36.270
We're not getting the bonus?

00:19:36.790 --> 00:19:37.720
He even says

00:19:38.030 --> 00:19:40.790
whatever was promised
before doesn't count.

00:19:41.310 --> 00:19:43.400
He runs Finance now.

00:19:43.720 --> 00:19:44.590
His word is final.

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:47.270
So our year-end bonus

00:19:48.440 --> 00:19:49.790
is dead in the water.

00:19:50.510 --> 00:19:51.480
How can he do that?

00:19:54.070 --> 00:19:55.110
I'll fight him!

00:19:55.350 --> 00:19:56.000
Stop!

00:19:57.030 --> 00:19:57.830
Are you crazy?

00:19:58.000 --> 00:19:58.880
Nobody's crazy.

00:19:59.880 --> 00:20:00.440
Liu Zhu,

00:20:00.680 --> 00:20:01.720
no way we just accept this.

00:20:01.830 --> 00:20:02.830
We're not pushovers!

00:20:03.070 --> 00:20:03.590
Qian!

00:20:03.790 --> 00:20:04.790
What? Am I wrong?

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:06.750
He's already pissed,
and you're adding fuel?

00:20:06.920 --> 00:20:07.350
Liu Zhu,

00:20:07.790 --> 00:20:08.790
put that down.

00:20:08.960 --> 00:20:09.640
Don't give Liu

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:10.550
a heart attack!

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:13.070
Anyway,

00:20:13.400 --> 00:20:14.750
I'll handle him!

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:15.590
Liu Zhu!

00:20:16.270 --> 00:20:17.160
Wanna go to jail?

00:20:17.350 --> 00:20:18.270
Want your kid

00:20:18.350 --> 00:20:19.270
to be fatherless?

00:20:20.030 --> 00:20:20.640
Hao Qianqian.

00:20:23.960 --> 00:20:24.790
Liu Zhu,

00:20:25.240 --> 00:20:26.480
don't risk your life.

00:20:26.480 --> 00:20:27.440
I'm scared.

00:20:28.030 --> 00:20:29.160
No, I...

00:20:29.480 --> 00:20:30.200
For our kid.

00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:38.830
Liu,

00:20:39.110 --> 00:20:40.110
don't worry.

00:20:40.270 --> 00:20:41.480
The leaders

00:20:41.510 --> 00:20:42.510
will be reasonable.

00:20:42.720 --> 00:20:43.270
Right.

00:20:43.750 --> 00:20:44.590
A company this big

00:20:44.750 --> 00:20:46.110
can't just break promises.

00:20:46.550 --> 00:20:47.550
That director

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:49.960
is doing exactly that.

00:20:50.270 --> 00:20:50.920
We can

00:20:50.920 --> 00:20:51.920
go to find other leaders.

00:20:52.110 --> 00:20:53.550
Maybe Mr. Hu?

00:20:54.160 --> 00:20:55.350
Mr. Hu went on a business trip

00:20:55.480 --> 00:20:57.200
this morning.

00:20:57.550 --> 00:20:59.270
Won't be back before
the Spring Festival.

00:20:59.790 --> 00:21:00.590
Did you

00:21:00.720 --> 00:21:01.510
sign anything

00:21:01.550 --> 00:21:02.480
about the bonus?

00:21:03.510 --> 00:21:05.310
No, we didn't.

00:21:05.880 --> 00:21:07.680
I was so careless.

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:09.200
Sorry to mess this up.

00:21:09.750 --> 00:21:10.790
Careless?

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:12.680
They played you!

00:21:13.350 --> 00:21:14.920
They're always

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:16.160
bossing us around,

00:21:16.350 --> 00:21:18.000
but useless when it counts.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:19.960
Zip your mouth!

00:21:20.400 --> 00:21:20.960
This can't

00:21:21.000 --> 00:21:22.240
just slide.

00:21:22.920 --> 00:21:24.200
But we need a plan.

00:21:27.790 --> 00:21:28.590
If you want it,

00:21:29.640 --> 00:21:30.720
go get it yourself.

00:21:31.750 --> 00:21:32.270
I...

00:21:33.790 --> 00:21:34.680
I'm out.

00:21:35.960 --> 00:21:37.720
That much money, and you're out?

00:21:38.590 --> 00:21:40.110
I worked my ass off this year.

00:21:40.480 --> 00:21:42.510
All for that bonus.

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:48.960
Be grateful.

00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:49.920
Shenzhen

00:21:50.160 --> 00:21:51.350
pays more

00:21:51.480 --> 00:21:52.440
than inland cities.

00:21:52.790 --> 00:21:53.680
Especially compared to

00:21:53.960 --> 00:21:55.270
our hometown.

00:21:56.160 --> 00:21:56.920
Back off

00:21:58.110 --> 00:21:58.880
a little,

00:21:59.510 --> 00:22:00.590
and things get easier.

00:22:00.790 --> 00:22:01.750
Peace is

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:03.160
all we need.

00:22:03.590 --> 00:22:04.640
Let's not

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:06.350
stir up more trouble.

00:22:06.920 --> 00:22:07.790
Okay?

00:22:09.030 --> 00:22:09.750
Liu,

00:22:10.400 --> 00:22:11.200
Zhu makes

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:12.030
a good point.

00:22:12.350 --> 00:22:14.160
That bonus is what we deserve.

00:22:14.830 --> 00:22:16.750
They did pay you.

00:22:17.070 --> 00:22:18.510
But we took on extra work

00:22:18.790 --> 00:22:20.400
on condition of a bonus.

00:22:20.590 --> 00:22:22.480
That's just basic fairness.

00:22:22.920 --> 00:22:23.310
Besides,

00:22:23.550 --> 00:22:24.590
even without a contract,

00:22:24.830 --> 00:22:26.400
we could still sue.

00:22:26.830 --> 00:22:28.030
Listen to you.

00:22:28.480 --> 00:22:30.680
Suing the company?

00:22:30.830 --> 00:22:32.270
Why not?

00:22:32.550 --> 00:22:33.880
The law protects

00:22:34.000 --> 00:22:35.200
people's rights.

00:22:35.550 --> 00:22:36.960
Who hasn't been cheated

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:38.830
when away from home?

00:22:39.400 --> 00:22:40.270
Anyway,

00:22:40.750 --> 00:22:41.960
that bonus

00:22:42.590 --> 00:22:44.480
was extra.

00:22:45.240 --> 00:22:46.400
If you ask me,

00:22:48.790 --> 00:22:49.720
just let it go.

00:22:51.200 --> 00:22:51.790
Zhu,

00:22:52.400 --> 00:22:53.480
you're my son.

00:22:54.310 --> 00:22:55.160
Are you letting it go?

00:22:55.440 --> 00:22:55.920
Liu Zhu,

00:22:57.030 --> 00:22:58.200
think carefully.

00:23:00.270 --> 00:23:01.270
Don't disappoint me.

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:03.270
I'm not a coward.

00:23:04.110 --> 00:23:04.920
I won't let my wife

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:05.920
look down on me.

00:23:06.920 --> 00:23:07.480
You!

00:23:23.200 --> 00:23:23.830
Enough.

00:23:24.960 --> 00:23:26.030
You two

00:23:26.200 --> 00:23:27.310
should go apologize

00:23:27.350 --> 00:23:27.960
to Liu.

00:23:28.240 --> 00:23:29.590
He's got his pride.

00:23:30.510 --> 00:23:31.440
Losing that bonus

00:23:31.720 --> 00:23:32.830
hurts him more than anyone.

00:23:33.590 --> 00:23:34.070
Zhu,

00:23:34.550 --> 00:23:35.270
he's on daily meds

00:23:35.400 --> 00:23:36.160
for blood pressure.

00:23:39.830 --> 00:23:41.510
Getting angry is bad for him.

00:23:41.880 --> 00:23:42.750
If you

00:23:42.750 --> 00:23:43.550
want him safe,

00:23:43.550 --> 00:23:44.550
apologize now!

00:23:45.400 --> 00:23:45.920
Qian,

00:23:47.240 --> 00:23:48.200
Wanzhi is right.

00:23:49.480 --> 00:23:51.160
Liu is your future father-in-law.

00:23:51.160 --> 00:23:52.030
Your baby's grandpa.

00:23:52.240 --> 00:23:53.680
If he has a health problem,

00:23:53.960 --> 00:23:55.400
how are you gonna get married?

00:23:56.240 --> 00:23:58.030
I really did go too far.

00:23:59.920 --> 00:24:00.440
Liu Zhu!

00:24:05.880 --> 00:24:06.830
Go cheer him up.

00:24:25.200 --> 00:24:25.830
All good?

00:24:29.830 --> 00:24:31.240
Pretty much.

00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:33.440
He said

00:24:33.640 --> 00:24:34.310
he feels bad

00:24:34.310 --> 00:24:35.830
for you two.

00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:36.720
Even though

00:24:36.830 --> 00:24:37.790
I'm not in the family,

00:24:37.920 --> 00:24:39.400
but he already treats me like family.

00:24:39.590 --> 00:24:40.880
He also promised

00:24:41.270 --> 00:24:43.000
to give us a nice wedding.

00:24:43.240 --> 00:24:43.790
In spring,

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:44.750
he's building us

00:24:44.830 --> 00:24:45.880
five new rooms.

00:24:46.240 --> 00:24:47.510
After that, he will

00:24:47.640 --> 00:24:48.310
sell the tractor

00:24:48.510 --> 00:24:50.510
and get us a minivan.

00:24:50.830 --> 00:24:51.960
But I think

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:53.960
he's just worried about his grandchild.

00:24:54.270 --> 00:24:55.160
Hao Qianqian,

00:24:55.640 --> 00:24:56.720
don't tell me

00:24:56.720 --> 00:24:57.830
you made a deal with him?

00:24:58.110 --> 00:24:58.750
No.

00:24:58.880 --> 00:25:00.030
He offered.

00:25:00.310 --> 00:25:01.110
Then what about

00:25:01.110 --> 00:25:02.070
the year-end bonus?

00:25:02.350 --> 00:25:03.110
They are

00:25:03.200 --> 00:25:04.240
both pushovers.

00:25:04.270 --> 00:25:05.400
What could I do?

00:25:05.480 --> 00:25:06.880
Just play along.

00:25:07.160 --> 00:25:08.070
That's not

00:25:08.110 --> 00:25:09.000
what you were saying.

00:25:09.550 --> 00:25:10.640
Then tell me, Wanzhi.

00:25:10.720 --> 00:25:11.350
What do I do?

00:25:11.510 --> 00:25:12.720
Fight for it.

00:25:12.720 --> 00:25:13.720
Yeah!

00:25:15.920 --> 00:25:17.590
We two talked it through.

00:25:18.030 --> 00:25:18.750
Listen.

00:25:19.000 --> 00:25:20.070
If we get back

00:25:20.070 --> 00:25:21.400
that bonus,

00:25:22.030 --> 00:25:23.400
you'll have a lot more respect

00:25:23.550 --> 00:25:25.350
in their family.

00:25:26.160 --> 00:25:27.550
Everyone will look up to you.

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:29.110
No doubt.

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:32.750
But it's not easy.

00:25:35.480 --> 00:25:36.310
(Attention.)

00:25:36.400 --> 00:25:38.400
(This year's travel rush has begun.)

00:25:38.960 --> 00:25:39.550
(Ticket lines)

00:25:39.640 --> 00:25:41.640
(are already forming)

00:25:41.720 --> 00:25:43.240
(at Luohu Train Station.)

00:25:43.920 --> 00:25:46.000
(Temporary ticket booths
at Shenzhen Stadium)

00:25:46.000 --> 00:25:46.880
(are open)

00:25:47.070 --> 00:25:48.880
(to make buying tickets easier.)

00:25:49.440 --> 00:25:50.880
(To all travelers,)

00:25:50.880 --> 00:25:52.720
(please keep your ID
and belongings safe)

00:25:52.830 --> 00:25:54.110
(and plan your time wisely.)

00:25:54.550 --> 00:25:55.270
That's it.

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:57.030
Takeout for all this?

00:25:57.240 --> 00:25:58.110
Might take a while.

00:25:58.680 --> 00:25:59.480
Fang Wanzhi,

00:26:02.510 --> 00:26:03.310
Fang Wanzhi,

00:26:03.480 --> 00:26:04.350
it's been a long time.

00:26:04.720 --> 00:26:05.550
Gao Xiang!

00:26:07.000 --> 00:26:08.200
The construction site

00:26:08.350 --> 00:26:09.640
has shut down.

00:26:09.750 --> 00:26:11.270
Better sign up fast.

00:26:11.480 --> 00:26:12.510
There's a perfect class

00:26:12.640 --> 00:26:13.510
during the holiday.

00:26:13.960 --> 00:26:15.550
Why are you always showing up?

00:26:16.270 --> 00:26:16.920
What?

00:26:19.590 --> 00:26:21.440
It's Spring Festival.
Say something nice.

00:26:21.920 --> 00:26:23.480
You should say something nice too.

00:26:25.920 --> 00:26:26.480
Who told you

00:26:26.480 --> 00:26:27.310
I work at a site?

00:26:27.960 --> 00:26:29.240
Hao Qianqian told me.

00:26:29.640 --> 00:26:30.030
Oh,

00:26:30.310 --> 00:26:31.350
you'd better

00:26:31.480 --> 00:26:32.480
have a talk with her.

00:26:32.830 --> 00:26:34.030
Education matters,

00:26:34.160 --> 00:26:35.310
but cheating is not allowed.

00:26:35.640 --> 00:26:36.270
She came to me

00:26:36.400 --> 00:26:37.640
and wanted a fake degree.

00:26:37.790 --> 00:26:38.720
I was really shocked.

00:26:38.960 --> 00:26:40.310
We should stay legal.

00:26:40.680 --> 00:26:41.830
Her foundation is weak.

00:26:42.000 --> 00:26:43.160
But if she studies hard,

00:26:43.310 --> 00:26:44.440
I believe there's a way

00:26:44.590 --> 00:26:45.200
to get

00:26:45.240 --> 00:26:46.070
a real degree.

00:26:46.350 --> 00:26:47.270
You already finished

00:26:47.350 --> 00:26:48.440
your task, didn't you?

00:26:48.680 --> 00:26:50.030
Why are you recruiting here?

00:26:50.110 --> 00:26:51.880
Just happened to see you

00:26:51.960 --> 00:26:53.350
and remembered

00:26:53.350 --> 00:26:54.240
your education.

00:26:54.440 --> 00:26:55.400
None of your business.

00:26:56.480 --> 00:26:57.110
Alright.

00:26:57.640 --> 00:26:58.920
New topic then.

00:26:59.480 --> 00:27:00.790
Did you get your ticket?

00:27:00.960 --> 00:27:01.790
Is it tough?

00:27:02.030 --> 00:27:02.960
Any thoughts

00:27:03.030 --> 00:27:04.000
about the travel rush?

00:27:04.160 --> 00:27:04.640
Tell me.

00:27:05.000 --> 00:27:06.110
What are you doing now?

00:27:10.270 --> 00:27:11.240
My another job:

00:27:11.310 --> 00:27:12.680
newspaper correspondent.

00:27:13.240 --> 00:27:14.880
The travel rush is
the hottest topic now.

00:27:15.000 --> 00:27:16.160
I wanna write a feature

00:27:16.270 --> 00:27:17.720
from the perspective

00:27:17.830 --> 00:27:18.510
of workers here.

00:27:21.270 --> 00:27:22.240
Anything else?

00:27:23.070 --> 00:27:24.070
Ever been a lawyer?

00:27:27.070 --> 00:27:28.720
I majored in law.

00:27:30.480 --> 00:27:31.790
Really?

00:27:31.960 --> 00:27:33.440
Of course.

00:27:35.880 --> 00:27:36.920
Help me with a lawsuit.

00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:38.440
Win it, and I'll pay you.

00:27:40.960 --> 00:27:41.680
Suing who?

00:27:50.070 --> 00:27:51.960
What are you doing?

00:27:52.160 --> 00:27:53.310
No work today.

00:27:53.350 --> 00:27:54.680
Why set an alarm?

00:27:54.830 --> 00:27:55.790
So annoying!

00:27:56.070 --> 00:27:56.920
Where's Wanzhi?

00:28:02.790 --> 00:28:04.270
Where did she go?

00:28:05.240 --> 00:28:06.790
See if her luggage is here.

00:28:07.070 --> 00:28:08.510
Hope she didn't already leave.

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:09.440
She still owes you

00:28:09.480 --> 00:28:10.350
1,000.

00:28:10.680 --> 00:28:11.680
What are you saying?

00:28:11.750 --> 00:28:12.680
After all this time,

00:28:12.720 --> 00:28:13.880
you still don't know her?

00:28:14.480 --> 00:28:15.680
Just kidding.

00:28:22.310 --> 00:28:23.960
Haven't even talked to them yet,

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:25.270
and you want to sue?

00:28:25.920 --> 00:28:27.000
When you were job hunting,

00:28:27.030 --> 00:28:27.960
it was very tough.

00:28:28.200 --> 00:28:29.310
They gave you a shot.

00:28:29.750 --> 00:28:31.200
You should be grateful.

00:28:31.440 --> 00:28:32.720
Who says I'm not?

00:28:33.110 --> 00:28:34.160
That's a different matter.

00:28:34.880 --> 00:28:36.440
The bonus was promised from the start.

00:28:37.030 --> 00:28:38.510
But you don't have a contract.

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:40.400
Verbal agreements are legally binding.

00:28:40.750 --> 00:28:41.680
Useless education.

00:28:43.160 --> 00:28:43.920
I know.

00:28:44.400 --> 00:28:45.550
But that's complicated.

00:28:45.920 --> 00:28:47.310
I'm not sure whether the court

00:28:47.440 --> 00:28:48.000
will hear it.

00:28:48.160 --> 00:28:48.640
Besides,

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:49.880
you have to wait in line.

00:28:50.480 --> 00:28:51.790
The court will gather evidence.

00:28:52.030 --> 00:28:53.590
But workers don't stay long there.

00:28:53.920 --> 00:28:54.720
You may not be able

00:28:54.790 --> 00:28:55.960
to find the witnesses.

00:28:57.270 --> 00:28:58.830
This case would be a real grind

00:28:59.110 --> 00:29:00.550
for any lawyer.

00:29:01.440 --> 00:29:02.830
And there's not much money in it.

00:29:03.590 --> 00:29:04.590
Hard to name

00:29:04.640 --> 00:29:05.350
a fair fee.

00:29:07.720 --> 00:29:09.110
Here's your takeout.

00:29:09.510 --> 00:29:10.110
Thanks.

00:29:11.680 --> 00:29:12.720
Now I see.

00:29:12.920 --> 00:29:14.310
You're all talk.

00:29:14.590 --> 00:29:16.160
I shouldn't have expected your help.

00:29:16.830 --> 00:29:18.160
Don't get upset.

00:29:18.400 --> 00:29:20.000
Let me analyze it more carefully.

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:21.400
Mr. Gao!

00:29:23.070 --> 00:29:24.030
My interviewee arrived.

00:29:24.070 --> 00:29:24.680
Maybe you could

00:29:24.790 --> 00:29:25.310
join us.

00:29:25.510 --> 00:29:26.270
After I'm done,

00:29:26.310 --> 00:29:27.110
I'll analyze

00:29:27.110 --> 00:29:27.790
your case.

00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:28.550
There might be

00:29:28.680 --> 00:29:29.480
other ways...

00:29:29.480 --> 00:29:30.550
Go do your thing.

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:31.510
Hope I don't

00:29:31.510 --> 00:29:32.110
see you again.

00:29:33.200 --> 00:29:33.550
You...

00:29:34.160 --> 00:29:35.350
Well, well.

00:29:45.160 --> 00:29:46.270
Where were you?

00:29:46.960 --> 00:29:48.030
The kitchen's closed.

00:29:48.200 --> 00:29:49.640
But we can't skip breakfast.

00:29:51.920 --> 00:29:52.880
Cantonese breakfast.

00:29:53.160 --> 00:29:54.480
Wide selection and delicious.

00:29:55.350 --> 00:29:56.920
I just brought some

00:29:56.920 --> 00:29:58.110
to Liu and Zhu too.

00:29:59.550 --> 00:30:01.030
Looks really good.

00:30:01.480 --> 00:30:03.000
Breakfast in the canteen is good too.

00:30:03.030 --> 00:30:03.720
But after a year,

00:30:03.720 --> 00:30:04.550
I'm sick of it.

00:30:05.680 --> 00:30:07.110
Wow, Wanzhi.

00:30:07.550 --> 00:30:08.160
Let's eat.

00:30:11.000 --> 00:30:12.200
You need to get to your train.

00:30:12.440 --> 00:30:13.200
After breakfast,

00:30:13.240 --> 00:30:14.160
you two go pack.

00:30:14.310 --> 00:30:15.160
I'm going to Finance.

00:30:16.350 --> 00:30:17.510
You still won't give up?

00:30:18.680 --> 00:30:19.880
For gradates' benefits,

00:30:19.920 --> 00:30:21.000
my mom spent her days

00:30:21.270 --> 00:30:23.110
running between the personnel, health,

00:30:23.200 --> 00:30:23.960
and labor bureaus.

00:30:24.440 --> 00:30:25.750
For farmers' subsidies,

00:30:25.920 --> 00:30:27.590
my dad stayed up late on applications.

00:30:27.920 --> 00:30:29.510
In the end, they both made it.

00:30:29.790 --> 00:30:30.590
This bonus

00:30:30.640 --> 00:30:31.640
is what we deserve.

00:30:32.070 --> 00:30:33.550
If I can't solve it in Shenzhen,

00:30:33.880 --> 00:30:34.750
I'll take a train

00:30:34.920 --> 00:30:35.790
to the headquarters.

00:30:36.110 --> 00:30:37.400
If not now,

00:30:37.590 --> 00:30:38.350
I'll wait

00:30:38.480 --> 00:30:39.440
till they return

00:30:39.550 --> 00:30:40.110
and carry on.

00:30:41.270 --> 00:30:42.550
Your nephew wrote one letter

00:30:42.550 --> 00:30:43.640
and you give him 5,000.

00:30:43.790 --> 00:30:45.110
I thought you were generous.

00:30:45.350 --> 00:30:47.000
So you also care about money.

00:30:47.240 --> 00:30:48.680
Who doesn't?

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:51.750
And it's not only

00:30:51.880 --> 00:30:52.550
about money,

00:30:52.720 --> 00:30:53.440
but about dignity.

00:30:53.640 --> 00:30:54.480
We have to fight.

00:30:55.160 --> 00:30:55.720
Wanzhi,

00:30:56.270 --> 00:30:57.400
that's exactly how I feel.

00:30:57.590 --> 00:30:58.480
I'm going with you.

00:31:00.750 --> 00:31:01.110
Then...

00:31:01.350 --> 00:31:02.270
I'm going too.

00:31:04.310 --> 00:31:06.400
But yesterday I promised Liu

00:31:06.550 --> 00:31:07.880
I wouldn't join you.

00:31:07.960 --> 00:31:08.750
He will get mad.

00:31:09.920 --> 00:31:11.590
Then are you going or not?

00:31:13.030 --> 00:31:13.790
If all three of us

00:31:13.830 --> 00:31:14.750
go together,

00:31:15.030 --> 00:31:16.590
we could make a plan.

00:31:18.680 --> 00:31:20.110
Fine, I'll go.

00:31:26.880 --> 00:31:27.830
I'll say it again.

00:31:28.640 --> 00:31:30.310
I really don't know anything

00:31:30.680 --> 00:31:32.550
about the year-end bonus.

00:31:33.110 --> 00:31:34.880
Go to the person

00:31:34.920 --> 00:31:36.480
who promised you.

00:31:36.790 --> 00:31:38.440
Wanna get money from me?

00:31:38.640 --> 00:31:39.440
Dream on.

00:31:40.030 --> 00:31:41.110
Go back.

00:31:41.960 --> 00:31:43.640
The bonus was promised

00:31:43.750 --> 00:31:44.640
by the last director.

00:31:44.680 --> 00:31:46.200
It's not coming out of your pocket.

00:31:46.310 --> 00:31:48.160
Why are you holding onto it so tight?

00:31:48.440 --> 00:31:50.400
Every penny is from the country.

00:31:50.920 --> 00:31:52.640
I'm doing this for
the company's interests.

00:31:52.880 --> 00:31:53.830
For the company,

00:31:54.030 --> 00:31:54.830
the best interest

00:31:55.000 --> 00:31:56.270
is to establish a good image

00:31:56.480 --> 00:31:57.240
in this city

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:58.400
that leads reform.

00:31:58.640 --> 00:32:00.000
Withholding bonuses

00:32:00.200 --> 00:32:01.240
is a huge harm

00:32:01.400 --> 00:32:02.310
to the company.

00:32:06.070 --> 00:32:06.880
Finished?

00:32:07.480 --> 00:32:08.160
Out! Now!

00:32:09.510 --> 00:32:10.110
Mr. Wang,

00:32:10.720 --> 00:32:11.510
something's wrong.

00:32:11.680 --> 00:32:12.960
A pregnant lady's making a scene!

00:32:16.550 --> 00:32:18.030
Shady company!

00:32:18.590 --> 00:32:20.400
Give back my money!

00:32:21.070 --> 00:32:22.510
Come out!

00:32:24.480 --> 00:32:24.920
I'll...

00:32:24.960 --> 00:32:26.070
What are you doing?

00:32:26.160 --> 00:32:27.640
Who sent you

00:32:27.750 --> 00:32:28.480
to sell pesticide?

00:32:28.680 --> 00:32:29.920
Who's selling pesticide?

00:32:30.160 --> 00:32:31.880
I'm here to drink it.

00:32:32.000 --> 00:32:33.400
Two lives.

00:32:33.510 --> 00:32:34.200
Oh no!

00:32:34.680 --> 00:32:35.310
Who are you?

00:32:36.270 --> 00:32:36.750
Qian,

00:32:37.030 --> 00:32:38.350
calm down.

00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:39.440
How can I calm down?

00:32:39.790 --> 00:32:40.880
The five of us

00:32:41.160 --> 00:32:42.000
cooked for

00:32:42.030 --> 00:32:43.070
over 300 people every day.

00:32:43.310 --> 00:32:44.440
All that hard work

00:32:44.590 --> 00:32:45.960
just for this bonus.

00:32:46.550 --> 00:32:48.110
But you broke your word!

00:32:48.550 --> 00:32:50.440
My parents are both in the hospital.

00:32:50.550 --> 00:32:51.350
If I don't get

00:32:51.400 --> 00:32:52.510
this money,

00:32:53.070 --> 00:32:55.030
I just can't go on anymore!

00:32:55.350 --> 00:32:56.200
- No!
- Qian!

00:32:56.480 --> 00:32:57.720
Please calm down!

00:32:57.880 --> 00:32:59.110
Director Wang says

00:32:59.270 --> 00:33:00.550
he will help us.

00:33:10.200 --> 00:33:11.270
I see now.

00:33:11.720 --> 00:33:12.750
You three

00:33:12.750 --> 00:33:13.720
are in on this together.

00:33:14.790 --> 00:33:15.480
Working together

00:33:15.640 --> 00:33:16.830
to extort me, huh?

00:33:17.350 --> 00:33:18.310
Go get security

00:33:18.350 --> 00:33:19.160
right now.

00:33:20.310 --> 00:33:20.720
What?

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.440
Is this how a leader behaves?

00:33:22.680 --> 00:33:24.000
Pushing people to the edge

00:33:24.200 --> 00:33:25.750
rather than keeping a promise?

00:33:26.350 --> 00:33:27.590
Listen, girls.

00:33:28.680 --> 00:33:31.070
You already make plenty.

00:33:31.400 --> 00:33:32.440
When I came from inland

00:33:32.590 --> 00:33:33.640
and saw your pay stubs,

00:33:33.680 --> 00:33:35.000
my heart trembled.

00:33:35.240 --> 00:33:36.880
Are you still not satisfied?

00:33:37.310 --> 00:33:38.350
If this were inland,

00:33:38.680 --> 00:33:40.000
only high‑ranking officials

00:33:40.160 --> 00:33:41.920
would make that much.

00:33:43.000 --> 00:33:43.790
So you think

00:33:43.830 --> 00:33:44.960
we earn too much?

00:33:45.680 --> 00:33:46.550
Don't you?

00:33:47.000 --> 00:33:47.790
You're

00:33:47.790 --> 00:33:48.960
temporary workers.

00:33:49.270 --> 00:33:49.880
No rank,

00:33:50.160 --> 00:33:50.750
no seniority.

00:33:51.030 --> 00:33:52.160
How much more do you want?

00:33:52.880 --> 00:33:54.030
You're so set

00:33:54.110 --> 00:33:55.310
in your old ways!

00:33:55.590 --> 00:33:57.200
You wanna equal distribution?

00:33:57.510 --> 00:33:58.590
This is the Special Zone!

00:33:58.790 --> 00:34:00.270
More work, more pay!

00:34:00.480 --> 00:34:01.790
Bonuses for overproduction!

00:34:02.240 --> 00:34:03.400
We rest

00:34:03.550 --> 00:34:04.880
less than eight hours a day.

00:34:05.110 --> 00:34:06.160
Our workload

00:34:06.310 --> 00:34:07.880
is double that of other canteens.

00:34:08.230 --> 00:34:09.630
Our food quality

00:34:09.880 --> 00:34:11.800
always ranks first.

00:34:12.800 --> 00:34:13.400
The bonus

00:34:13.550 --> 00:34:14.190
is 50%

00:34:14.320 --> 00:34:15.360
of our salary.

00:34:15.510 --> 00:34:17.630
The leadership said it!

00:34:18.110 --> 00:34:19.000
It must be honored!

00:34:19.480 --> 00:34:20.920
Or we'll keep fighting!

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:21.440
Yes!

00:34:21.590 --> 00:34:23.030
We'll fight to the end!

00:34:23.280 --> 00:34:24.000
No! Hurry!

00:34:24.550 --> 00:34:25.190
Come on, Qian!

00:34:25.190 --> 00:34:25.840
Qian!

00:34:25.920 --> 00:34:26.670
Security department!

00:34:27.230 --> 00:34:28.320
Put down the pesticide!

00:34:28.550 --> 00:34:29.630
Let's talk nicely.

00:34:29.840 --> 00:34:31.150
Talk nicely? No way!

00:34:31.150 --> 00:34:32.960
Have you ever talked nicely with me?

00:34:33.150 --> 00:34:34.190
I can't go on!

00:34:34.320 --> 00:34:36.360
Qian!

00:34:36.480 --> 00:34:38.110
No! Stop it!

00:34:44.000 --> 00:34:44.550
Mr. Hu,

00:34:44.840 --> 00:34:45.400
see.

00:34:52.550 --> 00:34:53.110
What's up?

00:34:53.550 --> 00:34:54.230
Li Juan,

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:55.630
what's she doing?

00:34:56.070 --> 00:34:56.710
Mr. Hu,

00:34:57.510 --> 00:34:58.070
didn't you

00:34:58.280 --> 00:34:59.030
already leave?

00:34:59.320 --> 00:35:00.110
I was about to.

00:35:01.000 --> 00:35:02.320
But Mr. Gao invited me

00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:03.880
to give a class.

00:35:04.070 --> 00:35:04.630
And today,

00:35:04.920 --> 00:35:05.670
at the station,

00:35:05.710 --> 00:35:06.510
he stopped me

00:35:06.840 --> 00:35:07.920
and said you were suing us.

00:35:09.360 --> 00:35:10.400
Yes, we're suing.

00:35:10.760 --> 00:35:11.590
Suing him.

00:35:12.110 --> 00:35:13.070
No, Mr. Hu.

00:35:13.400 --> 00:35:15.030
This has nothing to do with me.

00:35:15.360 --> 00:35:16.550
I've been following the rules.

00:35:17.070 --> 00:35:18.550
No matter how unreasonable they are,

00:35:18.880 --> 00:35:20.000
I won't give in.

00:35:22.360 --> 00:35:22.800
Well,

00:35:23.230 --> 00:35:23.920
clear the area.

00:35:25.670 --> 00:35:26.070
Wang,

00:35:27.000 --> 00:35:27.510
Fang Wanzhi,

00:35:28.590 --> 00:35:29.190
come with me.

00:35:34.070 --> 00:35:35.000
I briefed you on this

00:35:35.280 --> 00:35:36.190
before I left, right?

00:35:36.710 --> 00:35:37.590
Yes, you did.

00:35:38.670 --> 00:35:39.920
But there's no contract.

00:35:40.550 --> 00:35:41.840
That was our oversight.

00:35:42.230 --> 00:35:42.880
Sure,

00:35:43.360 --> 00:35:44.480
Liu isn't

00:35:44.710 --> 00:35:45.400
well-educated

00:35:46.070 --> 00:35:47.150
and not big on contracts.

00:35:47.510 --> 00:35:49.030
But anyway, their workload

00:35:49.320 --> 00:35:50.710
went up

00:35:50.960 --> 00:35:52.400
to meet the site's needs,

00:35:52.670 --> 00:35:54.190
so we added a year-end bonus.

00:35:54.960 --> 00:35:56.000
This was discussed

00:35:56.000 --> 00:35:56.920
at our meeting.

00:35:58.670 --> 00:35:59.710
You discussed it?

00:36:01.000 --> 00:36:01.960
But, Mr. Hu,

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:03.150
do you know

00:36:03.190 --> 00:36:04.230
how much they make?

00:36:04.510 --> 00:36:05.440
Of course.

00:36:05.670 --> 00:36:07.480
Their salary is not low.

00:36:12.920 --> 00:36:14.110
So that's the problem.

00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:16.440
It's your own mindset!

00:36:17.030 --> 00:36:18.590
Salaries are better here.

00:36:19.070 --> 00:36:20.510
But how do people here work?

00:36:21.550 --> 00:36:22.280
They start

00:36:22.800 --> 00:36:24.510
preparing breakfast at 4 AM.

00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:25.840
Their daily work hours

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:27.920
far exceed 12 hours.

00:36:28.400 --> 00:36:29.150
Have you

00:36:29.150 --> 00:36:30.000
investigated it?

00:36:30.880 --> 00:36:31.800
You see the pay.

00:36:32.760 --> 00:36:34.070
But the effort?

00:36:35.960 --> 00:36:36.510
Sorry.

00:36:37.670 --> 00:36:38.280
Mr. Hu,

00:36:38.880 --> 00:36:39.710
I was wrong.

00:36:40.320 --> 00:36:41.030
It's my first time

00:36:41.030 --> 00:36:41.510
working...

00:36:41.510 --> 00:36:42.280
Stop.

00:36:42.630 --> 00:36:43.480
Save the excuses.

00:36:44.360 --> 00:36:45.150
Sign a contract.

00:36:45.440 --> 00:36:46.320
Pay what's owed.

00:36:51.230 --> 00:36:52.280
To make it

00:36:52.800 --> 00:36:54.480
in the Special Zone,

00:36:55.150 --> 00:36:56.000
the key

00:36:56.320 --> 00:36:57.760
is keeping your word.

00:36:58.030 --> 00:36:58.760
Got it?

00:36:58.960 --> 00:36:59.510
Got it.

00:36:59.880 --> 00:37:00.670
I'll do it now.

00:37:04.480 --> 00:37:05.110
Fang,

00:37:06.110 --> 00:37:06.880
now,

00:37:07.030 --> 00:37:08.110
I'm gonna criticize you.

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:10.760
Problems should be
reported to higher-ups.

00:37:11.710 --> 00:37:12.880
Making a scene like this

00:37:13.150 --> 00:37:14.070
doesn't look good.

00:37:15.230 --> 00:37:16.710
And Li Juan is a soldier's wife.

00:37:17.110 --> 00:37:18.360
That makes it look even worse.

00:37:18.800 --> 00:37:19.960
It had nothing to do with her.

00:37:20.320 --> 00:37:21.110
It was my idea.

00:37:21.280 --> 00:37:22.360
She even tried to stop me.

00:37:24.280 --> 00:37:25.070
Go talk to her.

00:37:25.400 --> 00:37:25.920
That girl

00:37:26.110 --> 00:37:27.070
is holding pesticide.

00:37:34.280 --> 00:37:34.960
Qian.

00:37:36.150 --> 00:37:37.000
Put it down.

00:37:37.360 --> 00:37:37.880
Drink it.

00:37:38.590 --> 00:37:39.440
It's resolved?

00:37:41.110 --> 00:37:41.920
I knew it!

00:37:41.960 --> 00:37:43.150
My voice

00:37:43.400 --> 00:37:44.550
almost gave out.

00:37:45.880 --> 00:37:46.710
Relax.

00:37:48.280 --> 00:37:49.150
It's not pesticide.

00:37:52.510 --> 00:37:53.230
Mr. Hu,

00:37:53.550 --> 00:37:54.880
we couldn't find any leader.

00:37:54.960 --> 00:37:56.440
And they have a train to catch.

00:37:56.630 --> 00:37:58.230
We had no choice,

00:37:58.230 --> 00:37:58.670
so...

00:38:08.590 --> 00:38:09.000
Here.

00:38:10.110 --> 00:38:10.760
Okay?

00:38:13.030 --> 00:38:13.710
No good.

00:38:13.880 --> 00:38:14.880
Add some vinegar.

00:38:15.230 --> 00:38:16.670
I've been craving sour lately.

00:38:17.960 --> 00:38:19.030
Feels right.

00:38:28.360 --> 00:38:28.920
Mr. Hu,

00:38:29.230 --> 00:38:30.550
this tastes good.

00:38:30.590 --> 00:38:31.360
Want a taste?

00:38:32.840 --> 00:38:33.510
You really know

00:38:33.840 --> 00:38:34.880
how to cause trouble.

00:38:35.320 --> 00:38:35.920
Remember this

00:38:36.150 --> 00:38:37.000
and learn your lesson.

00:38:38.150 --> 00:38:38.920
This kind of method

00:38:39.150 --> 00:38:40.320
won't solve anything.

00:38:42.670 --> 00:38:43.400
Mr. Hu,

00:38:44.030 --> 00:38:45.150
sorry for the trouble.

00:38:46.230 --> 00:38:47.550
Hold on, Hao Qianqian.

00:38:47.710 --> 00:38:48.840
When did you get pregnant?

00:38:49.070 --> 00:38:50.150
Your belly grew fast.

00:38:52.030 --> 00:38:53.320
I'm really pregnant.

00:38:53.630 --> 00:38:55.760
But this belly...

00:38:59.670 --> 00:39:00.710
Had to make it big,

00:39:00.840 --> 00:39:01.960
or you wouldn't care.

00:39:08.360 --> 00:39:09.550
Thanks for today.

00:39:10.760 --> 00:39:11.710
Just a coincidence.

00:39:12.440 --> 00:39:14.110
I happened to invite Mr. Hu

00:39:14.280 --> 00:39:15.150
to teach a class.

00:39:16.070 --> 00:39:16.960
He's teaching

00:39:17.000 --> 00:39:18.110
the holiday class too.

00:39:18.590 --> 00:39:20.070
I really think it's perfect for you.

00:39:20.150 --> 00:39:21.320
Think it over?

00:39:21.550 --> 00:39:22.280
No.

00:39:25.230 --> 00:39:26.710
Then what will you do

00:39:26.960 --> 00:39:28.550
alone in Shenzhen?

00:39:28.880 --> 00:39:30.230
How do you know I'll be alone?

00:39:30.760 --> 00:39:32.110
How do you always know my things?

00:39:32.840 --> 00:39:33.590
Li Juan.

00:39:33.670 --> 00:39:34.840
Nonsense.

00:39:35.030 --> 00:39:36.110
Hao Qianqian might do that.

00:39:36.110 --> 00:39:36.760
But Li Juan?

00:39:36.800 --> 00:39:38.280
She's not the one to gossip.

00:39:38.510 --> 00:39:39.920
It really was Li Juan.

00:39:40.510 --> 00:39:41.230
I just asked

00:39:41.280 --> 00:39:43.150
about everyone's plans
for Spring Festival.

00:39:44.320 --> 00:39:45.440
Li Juan meant well.

00:39:46.070 --> 00:39:47.070
She was worried

00:39:47.110 --> 00:39:48.230
you'd be lonely.

00:39:48.800 --> 00:39:49.550
No need.

00:39:50.550 --> 00:39:51.920
I just wanna

00:39:51.960 --> 00:39:53.000
find a proper job.

00:39:53.360 --> 00:39:55.150
I can help you.

00:39:56.110 --> 00:39:57.400
Lots of employers recruit

00:39:57.400 --> 00:39:58.190
through the school.

00:39:58.510 --> 00:39:59.440
If you get your degree

00:39:59.510 --> 00:40:00.440
in six months,

00:40:00.550 --> 00:40:01.510
all these jobs

00:40:01.590 --> 00:40:02.760
will be open to you.

00:40:03.510 --> 00:40:04.510
Stop selling.

00:40:05.320 --> 00:40:06.400
Wait. Take a look.

00:40:06.670 --> 00:40:07.190
Just look!

00:40:08.190 --> 00:40:09.320
I'm here over the holiday.

00:40:09.510 --> 00:40:10.670
Leave me your number.

00:40:10.710 --> 00:40:11.480
Call me if needed.

00:40:11.670 --> 00:40:12.800
I don't need you.

00:40:24.150 --> 00:40:25.710
Gao Xiang is pretty solid.

00:40:26.280 --> 00:40:27.550
You really just ran into him?

00:40:27.630 --> 00:40:28.920
Didn't go looking?

00:40:29.110 --> 00:40:31.150
That's a big coincidence.

00:40:31.760 --> 00:40:33.110
I call it bad luck.

00:40:34.150 --> 00:40:36.230
I've always thought he's nice.

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:38.000
Why do you hate him?

00:40:39.510 --> 00:40:40.710
It's not hate.

00:40:41.320 --> 00:40:42.400
Every time we meet,

00:40:42.400 --> 00:40:43.150
he reminds me

00:40:43.190 --> 00:40:44.590
that I don't have a degree

00:40:44.960 --> 00:40:46.510
and tries to get me to sign up.

00:40:46.630 --> 00:40:48.030
So preachy.

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:49.110
Drives me nuts.

00:40:49.960 --> 00:40:52.070
Tough talk, but soft inside.

00:40:52.400 --> 00:40:53.030
Wanzhi,

00:40:54.030 --> 00:40:55.190
do you have feelings for him?

00:40:57.590 --> 00:40:59.320
Yeah, I have lots of feelings.

00:40:59.360 --> 00:41:00.150
What I feel most is

00:41:00.150 --> 00:41:00.630
I want him

00:41:00.670 --> 00:41:02.110
out of my sight.

00:41:12.320 --> 00:41:13.280
Here's the bonus.

00:41:13.960 --> 00:41:14.880
You four split it.

00:41:15.670 --> 00:41:16.230
Hold on.

00:41:17.400 --> 00:41:18.400
Why four?

00:41:18.400 --> 00:41:19.550
There are five of us.

00:41:21.960 --> 00:41:23.230
I don't deserve a cut.

00:41:24.800 --> 00:41:26.710
You three got the money back.

00:41:28.110 --> 00:41:30.190
Zhu wanted it too.

00:41:31.030 --> 00:41:32.920
If he can share with you,

00:41:33.590 --> 00:41:35.150
that's enough for me.

00:41:35.480 --> 00:41:36.110
No way.

00:41:36.440 --> 00:41:38.110
You're in charge of this canteen.

00:41:38.360 --> 00:41:39.590
You must take a share.

00:41:39.880 --> 00:41:40.360
Li Juan,

00:41:40.590 --> 00:41:41.070
Qian,

00:41:41.280 --> 00:41:41.880
do you agree?

00:41:42.150 --> 00:41:42.710
Yes.

00:41:43.190 --> 00:41:44.230
Liu worked the hardest.

00:41:44.480 --> 00:41:45.590
He deserves a cut.

00:41:45.920 --> 00:41:46.960
I agree even more.

00:41:47.190 --> 00:41:48.320
My father-in-law's money

00:41:48.590 --> 00:41:49.360
is going to help

00:41:49.360 --> 00:41:50.360
the two of us.

00:41:55.440 --> 00:41:56.360
See, Liu?

00:41:56.590 --> 00:41:57.550
We're all agreed.

00:41:58.400 --> 00:41:59.800
You're the leader. Come on.

00:41:59.920 --> 00:42:00.440
I...

00:42:01.920 --> 00:42:02.710
As planned,

00:42:02.960 --> 00:42:04.880
you present the bonuses.

00:42:10.440 --> 00:42:11.280
Well, this...

00:42:11.920 --> 00:42:13.710
this is awkward.

00:42:13.880 --> 00:42:14.360
Alright.

00:42:18.150 --> 00:42:19.230
Got all your stuff?

00:42:19.400 --> 00:42:19.920
All packed.

00:42:20.840 --> 00:42:21.590
Take it easy.

00:42:22.480 --> 00:42:23.760
Relax. If you leave anything,

00:42:24.030 --> 00:42:24.960
I'll save it for you.

00:42:25.000 --> 00:42:25.440
Okay.

00:42:25.760 --> 00:42:27.110
You're really something.

00:42:29.360 --> 00:42:30.960
Lots of people are going home.

00:42:31.480 --> 00:42:32.440
And rents are cheaper.

00:42:32.590 --> 00:42:33.920
So I want to rent

00:42:34.320 --> 00:42:35.110
a bigger house.

00:42:35.400 --> 00:42:36.150
Good.

00:42:36.400 --> 00:42:37.710
I trust your judgment.

00:42:38.440 --> 00:42:39.920
Save me a spot.

00:42:40.030 --> 00:42:41.110
I'll be back.

00:42:41.440 --> 00:42:43.320
Come on. Stop blabbering.

00:42:43.480 --> 00:42:44.360
You'll be back?

00:42:44.510 --> 00:42:46.000
Zhu might agree. And the kid?

00:42:46.030 --> 00:42:47.280
I don't care.

00:42:47.590 --> 00:42:49.360
I should have a backup plan.

00:42:49.510 --> 00:42:51.000
Who knows what his family's like?